                <h5 style="color: black">Cozinhar</h5>
                <p style="color: black">Selecione a receita a seu gosto</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/tutorial2.png" alt="Second slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light">
                <h5 style="color: black">Receita</h5>
                <p style="color: black">Verifique se tem os ingredientes necessários e é hora de começar o passo a passo</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/tutorial3.png" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light">
                <h5 style="color: black">Passo a passo</h5>
                <p style="color: black">Realize o passo e avance para o próximo passo</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/tutorial4.png" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light">
                <h5 style="color: black">Dúvida</h5>
                <p style="color: black">Selecione a dúvida para a esclarecer</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/tutorial5.png" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light">
                <h5 style="color: black">Ementa semanal</h5>
                <p style="color: black">Prepare as receitas para a semana</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>

